OL,3,CPipe band honours former member who
OL,4,Cdied after D-Day eighty years ago
OL,6,FDorothy Kelly now lives in Australia
OL,7,Fbut travelled back to Hawick for her
OL,8,Ffather's service. She told ITV Border:
OL,9,F"I just feel really privileged that we
OL,10,Fwere able to come here today because
OL,11,Fwe only found out about it just a few
OL,12,Fweeks ago.
OL,14,F"We weren't planning on coming to the
OL,15,FUK at all. Then we thought, it's not
OL,16,Fsomething we can miss."
