OL,3,CPipe band honours former member who
OL,4,Cdied after D-Day eighty years ago
OL,6,FLuca Armstrong, 17, now has the honour
OL,7,Fof playing Willie's bagpipes. "As part
OL,8,Fof the ceremony, we agreed to hand the
OL,9,Fpipes back to Dorothy while the wreath
OL,10,Fwas being laid," he said,
OL,12,F"It was meant to symbolise Dorothy
OL,13,Fseeing part of her father."
